lead_paragraph: Karim Benzema, the most effective striker in La Liga this season in terms of goals per minutes, is set to return for Real Madrid's home derby with Atletico Madrid on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Sharpshooting Benzema Fit to Return in Madrid Derby
